data.description:
This spacious 4-bed, 3-bath gem is the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting living room, complete with a cozy fireplace. Oversized windows throughout the home flood each room with natural light, creating a bright and airy atmosphere.

The owner's suite is a true retreat, boasting a walk-in closet and jetted tub where you can unwind and relax after a long day. With three additional bedrooms, there's plenty of space for family and guests.

The lower level features a spacious family room, providing an ideal space for gatherings and movie nights. And don't forget the basement bathroom, which is already roughed in and ready for your finishing touches.

This townhome is just a stone's throw away from walk-in access to Big Lake, making it a breeze to enjoy water activities and scenic views. A short walk from home and you'll discover a large public park and beach, perfect for picnics, sports, and soaking up the sun.
